				<ol style="list-style-type:lower-alpha;">
					<li>Lead content in coatings</li>
					<li>Accessories - including sleeping accessories and change table accessories</li>
					<li>Opening entrapment</li>
					<li>Sides deflection and strength</li>
					<li>Latching or locking mechanisms</li>
					<li>Non-rigid top rails</li>
					<li>Brackets that are affixed to top rails</li>
