					<li>Cords and Straps length</li>
					<li>Sides height</li>
				</ol>
			</li>
			<li style="margin-bottom:5px;">Removal of wheels or casters restriction</li>
			<li style="margin-bottom:5px;">Updates of test methods</li>
			<li style="margin-bottom:5px;">Other editorial changes</li>
