	<a href="/regulatory-updates/May-2017/may2017-eu-amendment-lower-lead" class="recapViewStory" style="float:right;">View Story</a>
	<a href="javascript://" class="learnmore" style="float:left;">Read More</a>
	<div style="clear:both;"></div>
	<div class="moretext">
		<p>In the directive, the following changes have been made to the migration limit of lead (See <a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/regulatory-updates/September-2016/europe-amendment-toy-safety" target="_blank">previous story in Regulatory Recap: September 2016</a>):</p>
